Subject: a certain subset of reports is disappearing from our web portal in NEA
Description: After an unknown but fairly short amount of time the NEA web portal removes our custom reports. Once we regenerate the reports they reappear back in the web portal
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom

After an unknown but fairly short amount of time the NEA web portal removes our custom reports. Once we regenerate the reports they reappear back in the web portal.

Cause

Conflict with how the reports were copied that possibly affected the report GUID. 

Resolution

Performed a standard copy/paste action to avoid conflicts with the report GUID.
